snippet: Graeme Storm of England had a hole in one and finished with a six-under-par 64 in the third round, taking the lead at the European Masters in Crans-Montana, Switzerland.
abstract: Graeme Storm of England takes the lead at the European Masters in Crans-Montana, Switzerland; other golf news noted.
